<gap reason="ellipsis" /> 
<supplied reason="subaudible">when</supplied> he came to besiege 
<supplied reason="explanation">
  <foreign>kai koṇṭu</foreign>
  <note>Literally: "seizing, surrounding".</note>
</supplied> Maṇikkal in Vēṇāṭu, alias Iḷaṅkuṉṟi in Vēṇāṭu.
                </p>
                
                
